AGT-2026 Infrastructure Update Summary

Date: 2026-03-27

Overview
Replaced the legacy backend notes in backend-integration/ with a new AWS-based webhook infrastructure for Stripe Payment Links. The new flow is:
Stripe Payment Link payment -> Stripe webhook -> API Gateway HTTP API -> Lambda -> Twilio SMS to the business owner.

