- Rebuilt backend-integration/ to use the requested structure:
  - terraform/
  - lambda/
  - scripts/
  - clients/
  - README.md
- Removed the old backend reference files:
  - backend-integration/GO-LIVE-STEPS.md
  - backend-integration/worker.js

