- Added backend-integration/terraform/providers.tf with:
  - Terraform version constraint >= 1.5.0
  - AWS provider ~> 5.0
  - Region sourced from var.aws_region
- Added backend-integration/terraform/variables.tf with all required and optional variables, including sensitive flags on secret values.
- Added backend-integration/terraform/main.tf with:
  - IAM role for Lambda
